# Development
the .devcontainer can be used to develop in vscode. it contains a Dockerfile and a devcontainer.json file. 
Use vscodes devcontainer-extension for development. you can run/debug/test your code inside the devcontainer.

# Production
the Dockerfile can be used to build a container for production and start the rest api
1. docker build -t bdccbackend . 
2. docker run -p 5000:5000 bdccbackend